{
  "stem": "27770.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this-- in this place, I cannot stay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whenever will be a first transport, they say, here they go a transport, there goes a transport, I said, whenever there's a transport first, I want to get out from here.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this is not a place-- here they will kill me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, there is a transport who goes to Melk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know how many kilometer was this Melk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I know, they took it with a train, and we arriving to a-- Melk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Melk, we arrive, evening, could be about 5 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there is the big, big camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people are going every day from this camp for a job.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Right away they told us, is not so easy here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "With wooden, wooden shoes, you have to go every day, 10 kilometer to the job, and 10 kilometer back from the job.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I figure I wouldn't be able to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And here, what I had trouble with my feet, you know, from all the wetness, and from all this, I got the green stuff on my feet.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I cannot walk with it anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm sick.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was-- they were there, Polish people, non-Jews, because of politic, whatever, they was against the German government.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took the whole families to camps, and between those people were older people and children, children 10 year old, 12 year old, 15 year old.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they was-- they took about 200 children to go in a kitchen to peel potatoes for the SS.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The potato has to be so clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If god forbid would be a point, you're finished.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was a little taller than the average children, but I figure myself, it's a little already close to evening.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
